======================================================================
BONUS: Why freed(v) connected + spanning => extreme score
======================================================================
freed(v) has cycles in W+ = {u:v->u} and W- = {u:u->v}
Cycles in W+ share no vertices with cycles in W- (partition)
No shared vertices => no shared edges => not adjacent
freed(v) connected => all in one side
freed(v) spanning V\{v} = W+ u W- => other side empty
=> score = 0 or n-1

